N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 326.6 - Procedure by commercial permit holders upon sale of restricted pesticides

State Regulations

Upon the sale by a commercial permit holder of a restricted
pesticide to a purchase permit holder the procedure for cancellation as
provided in section
326.10
of this Part shall be
followed. Notes
